<Content>Excellent Vacation Other posters have provided very detailed reviews so I won't bother writing redundant info. I would just like to say we went with an open mind expecting to run into a few issues after reading other reviews and also because the resort was open for only one week before our arrival. Issues during this period are typical  also the reason we were charged a low rate compared to rates we are seeing now, however... we did NOT have any problems during our 7 day stay. We met others who expressed issues with their rooms (majority seemed to be ground floor rooms) but ours was perfect, located on the second floor, reg suite, not in the Elegance Club. Service was outstanding from all staff we encountered. We enjoyed all restaurants (did not try Gourmet) and buffets. Out of all our vacations over the years this is the first time I felt the need to post a reivew. Guests during grand opening week who posted reviews expressed dissapointment and frustration but there seems to be a huge improvement in a short amount of time from what we've read and what we have seen for ourselves. We have enjoyed all of our Carribbean vacations, never returning to the same resort as we like try new properties each year but we absolutely insist on returning to ME some day. A huge thank you to the wonderful staff who went above and beyond their duty to ensure we had a wonderful vacation!! Looking forward to our next stay at ME. 
